      "temperament_early_childhood_decide_choiecs_opt_NA": "does not apply",
      "temperament_early_childhood_singing": "During daily or evening quiet time with you and your child, how often did your child enjoy just being quietly sung to?",
      "temperament_early_childhood_singing_opt_1": "never",
      "temperament_early_childhood_singing_opt_2": "very rarely",
